text: Renáta Štrbíková (born 6 August 1979) is a Czech table tennis player, born in Havířov. She competed in women's singles and women's doubles at the 2004 Summer Olympics in Athens. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:People from Havířov Category:Czech female table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of the Czech Republic Category:Table tennis players at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2015 European Games Category:European Games competitors for the Czech Republic Category:European Games medalists in table tennis Category:European Games bronze medalists for the Czech Republic
